# ─── Google OAuth Client ID ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get this from: https://console.cloud.google.com/
#   APIs & Services → Credentials → Create OAuth 2.0 Client ID
#
# Required setup before running:
#   1. Create a GCP project
#   2. Enable: Google Sheets API + Google Drive API
#   3. Create OAuth 2.0 Web Client ID
#      - Authorised JS origin: http://localhost:8080
#      - Authorised redirect URI: http://localhost:8080
#   4. OAuth consent screen → add scopes:
#      spreadsheets, drive.file, openid, email, profile
#   5. Add your email as a test user (while app is in "Testing" mode)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
